line_1: Charity may relax the miser's fist,
line_2: Arts once esteem'd may be with shame dismiss'd,

line_1: And spreads out his little black fist;
line_2: Ye niver seed yen sae distrest.

line_1: With thought-wing'd victory my untry'd fist:
Since by hardness of reason or hardness of fist
line_2: All wrong must be right if they choose to persist;

line_1: His lordship took each ploughman by the fist,
line_2: Drank to their sons, their wives, their daughters kiss'd;
